":16229,"position":19,"arabic":"١٤","translation":"(১৪)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":15,"arabic":"إِنَّمَآ أَمْوَٰلُكُمْ وَأَوْلَٰدُكُمْ فِتْنَةٌۭ ۚ وَٱللَّهُ عِندَهُۥٓ أَجْرٌ عَظِيمٌۭ","translation":"Your worldly goods and your children are but a trial and a temptation, whereas with God there is a tremendous reward.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5214.mp3","surahId":64,"words":[{"id":17379,"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّمَآ","translation":"মূলতঃ","audioUrl":"wbw/064_015_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":17380,"position":2,"arabic":"أَمْوَٰلُكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের মালগুলো","audioUrl":"wbw/064_015_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":17381,"position":3,"arabic":"وَأَوْلَـٰدُكُمْ","translation":"ও তোমাদের সন্তান সন্ততিরা","audioUrl":"wbw/064_015_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":17382,"position":4,"arabic":"فِتْنَةٌۭ ۚ","translation":"পরীক্ষা","audioUrl":"wbw/064_015_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":17384,"position":5,"arabic":"وَٱللَّهُ","translation":"এবং আল্লাহ্‌","audioUrl":"wbw/064_015_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":17385,"position":6,"arabic":"عِندَهُۥٓ","translation":"তাঁর কাছে (আছে)","audioUrl":"wbw/064_015_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":17386,"position":7,"arabic":"أَجْرٌ","translation":"প্রতিফল","audioUrl":"wbw/064_015_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":17387,"position":8,"arabic":"عَظِيمٌۭ","translation":"বড়","audioUrl":"wbw/064_015_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":17388,"position":9,"arabic":"١٥","translation":"(১৫)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":16,"arabic":"فَٱتَّقُوا۟ ٱللَّهَ مَا ٱسْتَطَعْتُمْ وَٱسْمَعُوا۟ وَأَطِيعُوا۟ وَأَنفِقُوا۟ خَيْرًۭا لِّأَنفُسِكُمْ ۗ وَمَن يُوقَ شُحَّ نَفْسِهِۦ فَأُو۟لَٰٓئِكَ هُمُ ٱلْمُفْلِحُونَ","translation":"Remain, then, conscious of God as best you can, and listen [to Him], and pay heed. And spend in charity for the good of your own selves: for, such as from their own covetousness are saved – it is they, they 